
Ical Converter Specifications

The Ical Converter conforms to these specifications:
    Ability to accept relatively messy/inconvenient ics files
    Ability to compile on most POSIX compliant systems
	Ability to generate HTML files readable by most Internet browsers.

The Ical Converter (icalconv) operates via a series of distributed bash and awk scripts.
Each script can be modified before making to suit the user's needs.